00:08:39.550 --> 00:08:40.601
Cinta.

00:08:41.338 --> 00:08:43.040
Cinta itu keras kepala.

00:08:45.129 --> 00:08:46.732
Gairah cinta.

00:08:47.152 --> 00:08:48.120
