Tidak peduli seberapa keras seseorang mencoba.

00:09:12.902 --> 00:09:14.791
Bondita dan Anirudh...

00:09:15.712 --> 00:09:17.147
Bondita dan...

00:09:18.621 --> 00:09:20.974
