akan datang bersama.

00:09:23.163 --> 00:09:24.535
Kami akan melakukannya, paman!

00:09:25.161 --> 00:09:27.122
Paman, menurutku, kamu...

00:09:27.567 --> 00:09:28.960
...panggil bandnya.

00:09:29.140 --> 00:09:31.204
Prosesi Barr...

00:09:32.786 --> 00:09:34.221
Dari Tuan Birristra.

00:10:07.230 --> 00:10:09.416
Saudari!

00:10:11.668 --> 00:10:12.905
Hai!

00:10:14.123 --> 00:10:15.228
Apa yang telah terjadi?

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:17.020
Apa yang kalian semua lakukan...

00:10:17.140 --> 00:10:18.807
