Kami sangat takut.

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:15.857
Ayo pergi dan cari Shashwati.

00:11:15.997 --> 00:11:17.225
Ayo pergi!

00:11:20.923 --> 00:11:22.886
'Aku akan menyatakan cintaku...

00:11:23.006 --> 00:11:25.043
